Nicean

Hi Nicean:

Well that would be quite a revelation–to learn that the minister’s children were in school and had access to a computer and a blog!

Since I am now firmly of the opinion that this is a piece of non-fiction, I will, at least for the moment, hold the suggestion that your staff position might be relevant. But, I do want to assure you that Rev. Hanson does not employ anyone on a permanent basis at her home; it would likely violate a number of employment laws in Ontario. So it is very unlikely that you would have seen Miss Hanson. However, since I now have a suspicion as to the identity of Rev. Hanson and Rev. Hanson (no?), you are advised to offer proof of employment should you decide – that is, should she call upon you to reveal your identity. That may be the safest course of action.

But, now I am very curious: Who is this blogger, and why do these two women post as they do?

Thanks for your inquiry.

–Barbara
